Access Permissions
Role	Can View	Can Edit	Can Dismiss Alerts	Notes
PEIMS Clerk	✅	✅	❌	Schedule steward only
Diagnostician	✅	✅	✅	SpEd alerts only
OT/PT/Speech	✅	✅	✅	Role-specific
Nurse	✅	✅	✅	Health alerts only
Admin	✅	✅	✅	Full campus view
Teachers	✅	❌	✅	Can dismiss, not edit
Paras	✅	❌	✅	Hygiene + escort alerts

What CoKeeper Is Not
Misuse Type	Clarification
Punitive Monitoring	❌ Not allowed. No behavior scoring, no compliance flags.
Performance Evaluation	❌ Not a rubric. No data used for teacher ratings or para reviews.
Surveillance	❌ No location tracking, no unauthorized access.
Alert Fatigue Generator	❌ Alerts are curated, not constant. No spam.
